subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: The driver’s Sprint Cup series-best sixth win of the season pushed Denny Hamlin past Jimmie Johnson for the top seed in the playoffs, which open next week at New Hampshire.
